description: DEMOLITION OF THE EXISTING BUILDINGS TO FACILITATE THE REDEVELOPMENT OF THE SITE AND THE PROVISION OF 89 RESIDENTIAL UNITS OF ACCOMMODATION (X7 FOUR BED, X13 THREE BED, X36 TWO BED, X33 ONE BED) IN BUILDINGS RANGING FROM THREE TO FOUR STOREYS IN HEIGHT, TOGETHER WITH ASSOCIATED CAR PARKING, CYCLE PARKING AND LANDSCAPING.
